         <abstract><p>There exist two distinct works under the title of Maṣḥafa faws manfasāwi, both penitential manuals for confessors having an Arabic origin.</p>
            <p><title ref="LIT4017Mashafa"/> was compiled by <persName ref="PRS7054Michael"/>, while <title ref="LIT4018Mashafa"/> was transmitted anonymously.
