         <div type="edition">
           <listBibl type="secondary">
              <bibl><ptr target="bm:Kleiner2000Faws"/> <citedRange unit="page">35</citedRange></bibl>
           </listBibl>
            
            <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="Introduction">
               <label>Introduction, consisting either of one or three chapters</label>
               
               <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="Introduction1">
                  <label>Introduction, chapter 1</label>
                  <desc>The content of this introduction corresponds exactly to <title ref="LIT4017Mashafa#Chapter1"/>, 
                  but the gǝʿǝz wording is completely different.</desc>
               </div>
               
               <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="Introduction2">
                  <label>Introduction, chapter 2: ካልእ፡ ጾታ፡ መጽሐፍ፡</label>
                  <desc>The first half of this chapter is identical to <title ref="LIT4017Mashafa#Chapter2"/>.
                  The second half is a translation of the treatise faṣl fī faḍīlat al-iʿtirāf wa-taṯbītihī.
                  <listBibl type="secondary">
                     <bibl><ptr target="bm:Kleiner2000Faws"/><citedRange unit="page">28-30</citedRange></bibl>
                  </listBibl>
                  <listBibl type="editions">
                     <bibl><ptr target="bm:Coeln1908Nomokanon3"/><citedRange unit="page">216-229</citedRange></bibl> <!--Arabic-->
                  </listBibl></desc>
               </div>
               
               <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="Introduction3">
                  <head><title xml:id="t3">ነገር፡ ዘከመ፡ እፎ፡ ይደሉ፡ ለዐቃቤ፡ ሥራይ፡ አእምሮ፡</title>
                     <title xml:id="t3arabic">faṣl fī-mā yaǧibu ʿalā ṭ-ṭabīb maʿrifatihī ʾaʿnī muʿallim al-iʿtirāf</title></head>
                  <desc> The third chapter contains the translation of the treatise faṣl fī-mā yaǧibu ʿalā ṭ-ṭabīb maʿrifatihī ʾaʿnī muʿallim al-iʿtirāf.
                     <listBibl type="editions">
                        <bibl><ptr target="bm:Coeln1908Nomokanon3"/><citedRange unit="page">210-217</citedRange></bibl> <!--Arabic-->
                     </listBibl>
                     <listBibl type="relations">
                        <bibl/>
                        <relation name="saws:isVersionInAnotherLanguageOf" active="LIT4018Mashafa#Introduction3" passive="LIT4018Mashafa#t3arabic"/>
                     </listBibl>
                  </desc>
               </div>
            </div>
            
            <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="QanonaHebu">
               <label>ቀኖና፡ ኅቡእ፡</label>
               <desc>Exhortations and canons attributed to <persName ref="PRS11239Theodorus"/>, divided into ca. 25 parts.</desc>
               <listBibl type="relations">
                  <bibl/>
                  <relation name="saws:isAttributedToAuthor" active="LIT4018Mashafa#QanonaHebu" passive="PRS11239Theodorus"/>
               </listBibl>
               
               <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="QanonaHebu1">
                  <label>First part of canons and exhortations attributed to <persName ref="PRS11239Theodorus"/>.</label>
                  <listBibl type="relations">
                     <bibl/>
                     <relation name="saws:isAttributedToAuthor" active="LIT4018Mashafa#QanonaHebu" passive="PRS11239Theodorus"/>
                  </listBibl>
               </div>
                  
               <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="Homosexuality">
                  <label>ነገር፡ በእንተ፡ ዘይሰብክ፡ ተባዕተ፤ ወውእቱ፡ ዲበ፡ ፫ <sic>ዘዘዚአሁ</sic>።</label>
                  <desc>Treatise on three variants of homosexuality included in <title ref="LIT4018Mashafa#QanonaHebu"/></desc>
               </div>
            </div>
            
            <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="QanonaHebu2">
